<style>
    .test { background-color: red; width: 2147483648em; height: 12em; }
    .test { background-color: oklch(51.975% 44.1% 142.495); } /* green (sRGB #7999) converted to OKLCH */
</style>
<body>
    <p>Test passes if you see a green square, and no red.</p>
